\f1\b0\fs44 \cf0     \'95	2 cups lightly packed baby spinach leaves (about 2 ounces)\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/4 cup pine nuts, toasted\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 tablespoons fresh lemon juice\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 to 2 teaspoons grated lemon peel\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/3 cup plus 2 teaspoons olive oil\
